Package nz.ac.vuw.ecs.swen225.gp22.domain

package nz.ac.vuw.ecs.swen225.gp22.domain
This module is responsible for representing and maintaining the current state of the game, such as what types of objects there are and which actions are allowed to change the state of those objects.
  • Class
    Description
    Actor
    Represents Actors in the game.
    Collectable
    Represents entities that the Player is able to pick up.
    Direction
    Directions that the Actor is able to move.
    Door
    Represents Doors in the game they can be opened by a Player.
    Entity
    Methods needed by all Entities in the game.
    Entity.Colours
    Holds Door and Key sprite that goes with each colour.
    EntityFactory
    Allows Entities to be created from external classes.
    Exit
    Represents the Exit in the game.
    ExitDoor
    Represents the Exit Door in the game.
    FloorTile
    Represents a FloorTile in the game.
    InfoTile
    Represents Info Tile in the game.
    Key
    Represents Keys in the game.
    LavaTile
    Represents a SewageTile in the game.
    LockedDoor
    Represents a locked door.
    Player
    Represents the Player in the game.
    Point
    Represents points used to control where Entities are in the game.
    Robot
    Represents Robot for level 2 of the game.
    Tile
    Represents tiles in the game.
    Treasure
    Represents the Treasure that can be picked up by the Player.
    WallTile
    Represents the Walls in the game.
